1.) Install GitLyn from the zipped archived  (Window > Install New Software... > Add > Archive...)
- Make sure to uncheck "Group items by category"

2.) Follow one of the ways to active JDT weaving outlined at
http://wiki.eclipse.org/JDT_weaving_features#Turning_on_JDT_Weaving_manually

3.) If it does not work for you, contribute resources to bug #329515:
https://bugs.eclipse.org/329515

